<exercise id="fs-id1164564771224">
<problem id="fs-id1164566496186">
<para id="fs-id1164565103792">Examine the differences and similarities in the structural features of animal and plant cells. <emphasis effect="bold">Justify the claim</emphasis> that both animals and plants have common ancestors based on your observations.</para>
